{
  "video_id": "nQcgD5DpVlQ",
  "title": "Why sex really matters | David Page | TEDxBeaconStreet",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 14859.0,
      "end_time": 21710.0,
      "text": "I would like to talk with you about sex and disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 21710.0,
      "end_time": 25451.0,
      "text": "but perhaps not what you're thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 25451.0,
      "end_time": 27611.0,
      "text": "So, now that I've gotten your attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 27611.0,
      "end_time": 31149.0,
      "text": "I'd like to tell you about  something that's really fundamental."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 31149.0,
      "end_time": 35668.0,
      "text": "I'd like to tell you about a connection between sex"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 35668.0,
      "end_time": 39201.0,
      "text": "and disease that is very critical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 39201.0,
      "end_time": 41771.0,
      "text": "but a connection between sex and disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 41771.0,
      "end_time": 45599.0,
      "text": "that has gone largely unnoticed and unexplored"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 45599.0,
      "end_time": 48796.0,
      "text": "even in within the scientific community."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 48796.0,
      "end_time": 51299.0,
      "text": "So, to get things under way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 51299.0,
      "end_time": 55409.0,
      "text": "let me open with three observations"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 55409.0,
      "end_time": 60095.0,
      "text": "that I think you may find  a little surprising and startling."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 60095.0,
      "end_time": 63924.0,
      "text": "First of all, human genome, we have a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 63924.0,
      "end_time": 68176.0,
      "text": "Second, men and women are not equal."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 68176.0,
      "end_time": 70510.0,
      "text": "I'll pause there --"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 70510.0,
      "end_time": 73755.0,
      "text": "And third, that the study of disease is flawed."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 73755.0,
      "end_time": 78563.0,
      "text": "So, let's explore each of these in turn."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 78563.0,
      "end_time": 80749.0,
      "text": "Across the course of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 80749.0,
      "end_time": 84160.0,
      "text": "scientists, no matter how brilliant they are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 84160.0,
      "end_time": 87788.0,
      "text": "have gotten things wrong in a big way."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 87788.0,
      "end_time": 92774.0,
      "text": "For a long time, we thought that the Earth was flat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 92774.0,
      "end_time": 97458.0,
      "text": "and we thought that  the sun revolved around the Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 97458.0,
      "end_time": 102228.0,
      "text": "Well, in this time of the human genome revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 102228.0,
      "end_time": 104967.0,
      "text": "it turns out that we're missing something"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 104967.0,
      "end_time": 107568.0,
      "text": "that is of critical importance."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 107568.0,
      "end_time": 110030.0,
      "text": "And to understand what's that all about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 110030.0,
      "end_time": 114541.0,
      "text": "I need to ask you to return with me to the beginning"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 114541.0,
      "end_time": 118141.0,
      "text": "where each of us began."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 118141.0,
      "end_time": 124348.0,
      "text": "So, here it is, the moment of conception, egg meets sperm!"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 124348.0,
      "end_time": 127099.0,
      "text": "All the cells of your body --"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 127099.0,
      "end_time": 130835.0,
      "text": "your lung cells, your liver cells, your skin cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 130835.00000000001,
      "end_time": 136655.0,
      "text": "all the cells of your body ultimately derived from this one founding cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 136655.0,
      "end_time": 139022.0,
      "text": "the fertilized egg."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 139022.0,
      "end_time": 143765.0,
      "text": "So, the fertilized egg divides to become two cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 143765.0,
      "end_time": 147708.0,
      "text": "those two divide to become four, and eight, and so on --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 147708.0,
      "end_time": 152017.0,
      "text": "until your entire body consisting of --"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 152017.0,
      "end_time": 156332.0,
      "text": "on the order of 10 trillion cells has been assembled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 156332.0,
      "end_time": 159847.0,
      "text": "and what is most amazing  is that within the nucleus"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 159847.0,
      "end_time": 164093.0,
      "text": "of each of those 10 trillion cells that make up your body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 164093.0,
      "end_time": 166569.0,
      "text": "within each of those cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 166569.0,
      "end_time": 172646.0,
      "text": "you carry the same 23 pairs of chromosomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 172646.0,
      "end_time": 175661.0,
      "text": "And those 23 pairs of chromosomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 175661.0,
      "end_time": 177532.0,
      "text": "carry all of the DNA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 177532.0,
      "end_time": 180935.0,
      "text": "all of the hereditary material,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 180935.0,
      "end_time": 183908.0,
      "text": "all of the hereditary information"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 183908.0,
      "end_time": 189634.0,
      "text": "with which your cells, and tissues,  and organs in your body execute their functions."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 189634.0,
      "end_time": 197128.0,
      "text": "So, let's look at those 23 pairs of chromosomes in more detail."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 197128.0,
      "end_time": 200896.0,
      "text": "It turns out, that of the 23 pairs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 200896.0,
      "end_time": 204457.0,
      "text": "22 pairs are absolutely identical"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 204457.0,
      "end_time": 207636.0,
      "text": "and shared between men and women."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 207636.0,
      "end_time": 209486.0,
      "text": "And here they're shown --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 209486.0,
      "end_time": 213264.0,
      "text": "The differences arise in the 23rd pair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 213264.0,
      "end_time": 219820.0,
      "text": "which in females is a beautifully matched  pair of X chromosomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 219820.0,
      "end_time": 224363.0,
      "text": "but in males, that 23rd matched pair"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 224363.0,
      "end_time": 230940.0,
      "text": "is replaced by a mismatched pair, an XY pair."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 230940.0,
      "end_time": 239440.0,
      "text": "And let's look in more detail  at that mismatched XY pair --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 239440.0,
      "end_time": 241238.0,
      "text": "Here they are --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 241238.0,
      "end_time": 246787.0,
      "text": "to the left, the stately  and grand X chromosome --"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 246787.0,
      "end_time": 250866.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) Why do you laugh?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 250866.0,
      "end_time": 259891.0,
      "text": "To its right, the diminutive and demure Y chromosome, with its head down."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 259891.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261964.00000000003,
      "text": "Now, if truth be known,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 261964.0,
      "end_time": 267888.0,
      "text": "I've spent the entirety of my career at Whitehead Institute"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 267888.0,
      "end_time": 272640.0,
      "text": "defending the honor of the Y chromosome -- (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 272640.0,
      "end_time": 278862.0,
      "text": "In the face of innumerable insults to its character and its future prospect."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 278862.0,
      "end_time": 286658.0,
      "text": "Even to this day, it is thought by physicians and most scientists around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 286658.0,
      "end_time": 288969.0,
      "text": "that the function of the Y chromosome"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 288969.0,
      "end_time": 294135.0,
      "text": "is restricted to the cells of the reproductive tract."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 294135.0,
      "end_time": 299798.0,
      "text": "And in fact, this idea that the cells of the reproductive tract"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 299798.0,
      "end_time": 301839.0,
      "text": "are the only place where the Y functions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 301839.0,
      "end_time": 304892.0,
      "text": "has led, in turn, to the notion"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 304892.0,
      "end_time": 309250.0,
      "text": "that the genomes of men and women are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 309250.0,
      "end_time": 311509.0,
      "text": "apart from the reproductive tract,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 311509.0,
      "end_time": 317470.0,
      "text": "functionally, maybe even morally equivalent."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 317470.0,
      "end_time": 323073.0,
      "text": "And so, in fact,  it has been said many times"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 323073.0,
      "end_time": 327178.0,
      "text": "that apart from the reproductive tract and even disregarding that for a moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 327178.0,
      "end_time": 328895.0,
      "text": "it is been said many times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 328895.0,
      "end_time": 333270.0,
      "text": "that our genomes are all 99.9% identical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 333270.0,
      "end_time": 336775.0,
      "text": "from one person to the next."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 336775.0,
      "end_time": 341972.0,
      "text": "This idea that we're 99.9% identical has gained great traction"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 341972.0,
      "end_time": 343631.0,
      "text": "and for a number of reasons --"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 343631.0,
      "end_time": 348090.0,
      "text": "It's very appealing to say that we are all 99.9% identical --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 348090.0,
      "end_time": 350616.0,
      "text": "It's so appealing that this idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 350616.0,
      "end_time": 354278.0,
      "text": "was seized upon by President Bill Clinton"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 354278.0,
      "end_time": 359511.0,
      "text": "in his 2000 State of the Union address --"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 359511.0,
      "end_time": 363615.0,
      "text": "when he stated that, \"This fall, at the White House..."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 363615.0,
      "end_time": 366337.0,
      "text": "we had a distinguished scientist visiting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 366337.0,
      "end_time": 369280.0,
      "text": "an expert in this work on the human genome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 369280.0,
      "end_time": 373581.0,
      "text": "and he said that we are all, regardless of race,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 373581.0,
      "end_time": 379711.0,
      "text": "genetically 99.9% the same.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 379711.0,
      "end_time": 384756.0,
      "text": "Wow -- it turns out that this idea is even correct --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 384756.0,
      "end_time": 393072.0,
      "text": "as long as, the two individuals being compared are both men."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 393072.0,
      "end_time": 402024.0,
      "text": "It's also correct, if the two individuals being compared are both women."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 402024.0,
      "end_time": 406808.0,
      "text": "However, if you compare the genome of a man"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 406808.0,
      "end_time": 408912.0,
      "text": "with the genome of a woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 408912.0,
      "end_time": 414259.0,
      "text": "you'll find that they are actually only 98.5% identical."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 414259.0,
      "end_time": 419439.0,
      "text": "In other words, the genetic difference between a man and a woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 419439.0,
      "end_time": 422866.0,
      "text": "is 15 times the genetic difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 422866.0,
      "end_time": 427823.0,
      "text": "between two men or between two women."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 427823.0,
      "end_time": 437255.0,
      "text": "Let us consider, for example, the case of Bill and Hillary -- (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 437255.0,
      "end_time": 446941.0,
      "text": "So, it turns out that Bill is as genetically similar to Hillary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 446941.0,
      "end_time": 456664.0,
      "text": "as he is to a male chimpanzee. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 456664.0,
      "end_time": 461344.0,
      "text": "But, human genome, we have a problem --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 461344.0,
      "end_time": 465051.0,
      "text": "In the human genome era in which we're living,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 465051.0,
      "end_time": 470116.0,
      "text": "this fundamental difference between males and females,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 470116.0,
      "end_time": 471946.0,
      "text": "has been overlooked."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 471946.0,
      "end_time": 474859.0,
      "text": "Instead, we have been operating"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 474859.0,
      "end_time": 479626.0,
      "text": "with a unisex vision of the human genome."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 479626.0,
      "end_time": 491482.0,
      "text": "And so -- in fact, men and women  are not equal in their genomes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 491482.0,
      "end_time": 493358.0,
      "text": "as I just explained,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 493358.0,
      "end_time": 495681.0,
      "text": "and, as I want to go on to explain now --"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 495681.0,
      "end_time": 501050.0,
      "text": "men and women are also not equal in the face of disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 501050.0,
      "end_time": 502975.0,
      "text": "Now, what do I mean by that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 502975.0,
      "end_time": 504736.0,
      "text": "And what are its consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 504736.0,
      "end_time": 507244.0,
      "text": "and what are the implications for health care?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 507244.0,
      "end_time": 511510.0,
      "text": "I will cite a number of examples to illustrate what I have in mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 511510.0,
      "end_time": 515566.0,
      "text": "We'll take the case of Rheumatoid Arthritis --"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 515566.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519095.00000000006,
      "text": "For every man with Rheumatoid Arthritis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 519095.0,
      "end_time": 524065.0,
      "text": "there are 2 to 3 women  who are affected with this disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 524065.00000000006,
      "end_time": 529693.0,
      "text": "Now, is Rheumatoid Arthritis  a disease of the reproductive tract?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 529693.0,
      "end_time": 530990.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 530990.0,
      "end_time": 536746.0,
      "text": "Is there any obvious anatomic difference between men and women"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 536746.0,
      "end_time": 540252.0,
      "text": "to account for this dramatic difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 540252.0,
      "end_time": 545320.0,
      "text": "in the incidence of Rheumatoid Arthritis, its higher incidence in women?"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 545320.0,
      "end_time": 549832.0,
      "text": "There is no simple,  anatomic explanation to be had."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 549832.0,
      "end_time": 555733.0,
      "text": "Let's flip the tables now and consider Autism Spectrum Disorders."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 555733.0,
      "end_time": 560009.0,
      "text": "For every girl with an Autism Spectrum Disorder"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 560009.0,
      "end_time": 562105.0,
      "text": "the most recent numbers suggest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 562105.0,
      "end_time": 567075.0,
      "text": "that there are about 5 boys with such a disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 567075.0,
      "end_time": 569636.0,
      "text": "Why is that the case?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 569636.0,
      "end_time": 573791.0,
      "text": "Let's flip the table yet again --"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 573791.0,
      "end_time": 579706.0,
      "text": "Lupus - a long term, autoimmune disorder"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 579706.0,
      "end_time": 583893.0,
      "text": "with devastating consequences that can result in death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 583893.0,
      "end_time": 589201.0,
      "text": "for every man who is suffering from Lupus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 589201.0,
      "end_time": 595046.0,
      "text": "there are 6 women who is suffering from this disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 595046.0,
      "end_time": 599135.0,
      "text": "And so, for a whole host of disorders"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 599135.0,
      "end_time": 602584.0,
      "text": "that occur outside the reproductive tract"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 602584.0,
      "end_time": 606484.0,
      "text": "we see that the incidence or prevalence"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 606484.0,
      "end_time": 610453.0,
      "text": "in men and women can differ dramatically."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 610453.0,
      "end_time": 613924.0,
      "text": "And even in the case when a disease occurs"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 613924.0,
      "end_time": 616090.0,
      "text": "in both men and women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 616090.0,
      "end_time": 619976.0,
      "text": "that disorder can be much more severe"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 619976.0,
      "end_time": 622453.0,
      "text": "or have more severe consequences"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 622453.0,
      "end_time": 625079.0,
      "text": "in one sex than the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 625079.0,
      "end_time": 630063.0,
      "text": "Let's consider here  the case of Dilated Cardiomyopathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 630063.0,
      "end_time": 632735.0,
      "text": "Dilated Cardiomyopathy is a condition"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 632735.0,
      "end_time": 636272.0,
      "text": "where the wall of the heart thins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 636272.0,
      "end_time": 641060.0,
      "text": "and the heart balloons dangerously --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 641060.0,
      "end_time": 644935.0,
      "text": "and sometimes, with  devastating consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 644935.0,
      "end_time": 648291.0,
      "text": "What I'm going to show you here  is the survival curve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 648291.0,
      "end_time": 650686.0,
      "text": "the death curve, if you will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 650686.0,
      "end_time": 654140.0,
      "text": "for women who have Dilated Cardiomyopathy"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 654140.0,
      "end_time": 658826.0,
      "text": "due to a very specific genetic defect --"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 658826.0,
      "end_time": 663585.0,
      "text": "It turns out that men can also get Dilated Cardiomyopathy"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 663585.0,
      "end_time": 667398.0,
      "text": "as a result of this same  specific genetic defect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 667398.0,
      "end_time": 672209.0,
      "text": "but if they do, they tend to die at a much younger age."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 672209.0,
      "end_time": 674951.0,
      "text": "Why is this the case?"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 674951.0,
      "end_time": 677755.0,
      "text": "Well, so I asked my colleagues --"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 677755.0,
      "end_time": 681254.0,
      "text": "When I travel around, I ask my colleagues  in biomedical research --"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 681254.0,
      "end_time": 685604.0,
      "text": "Why is it, that for so many disorders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 685604.0,
      "end_time": 688757.0,
      "text": "the incidence of disease or the severity of disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 688757.0,
      "end_time": 691852.0,
      "text": "differs so dramatically between men and women?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 691852.0,
      "end_time": 694089.0,
      "text": "Why is this the case?"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 694089.0,
      "end_time": 700356.0,
      "text": "And the answer, that I almost invariably get is --"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 700356.0,
      "end_time": 703755.0,
      "text": "\"I don't have a clue.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 703755.0,
      "end_time": 706501.0,
      "text": "Now, this is a big question --"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 706501.0,
      "end_time": 708160.0,
      "text": "this is a big, big question --"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 708160.0,
      "end_time": 711751.0,
      "text": "Whenever I press harder on my colleagues and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 711751.0,
      "end_time": 715211.0,
      "text": "What do you think might be going on?"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 715211.0,
      "end_time": 717792.0,
      "text": "The answer that I receive, most frequently is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 717792.0,
      "end_time": 723080.0,
      "text": "\"Well, maybe it's the sex hormones.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 723080.0,
      "end_time": 729546.0,
      "text": "How could it be that we are  in such a place in the research world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 729546.0,
      "end_time": 732201.0,
      "text": "in this, human genetics era"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 732201.0,
      "end_time": 735711.0,
      "text": "when the answers are so shallow?"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 735711.0,
      "end_time": 740363.0,
      "text": "Well, it turns out that  the human genetics revolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 740363.0,
      "end_time": 745907.0,
      "text": "has delivered us, has provided us with a set of tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 745907.0,
      "end_time": 748579.0,
      "text": "with which we can ask the question --"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 748579.0,
      "end_time": 752192.0,
      "text": "Why is one man at a higher or  a lower risk than another man"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 752192.0,
      "end_time": 756551.0,
      "text": "of suffering from a particular disease?"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 756551.0,
      "end_time": 760162.0,
      "text": "Similarly, we have the tools with which to ask the question --"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 760162.0,
      "end_time": 764246.0,
      "text": "Why is one woman at a higher or  a lower risk than another woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 764246.0,
      "end_time": 766149.0,
      "text": "of suffering from a particular disease?"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 766149.0,
      "end_time": 769990.0,
      "text": "But, as unbelievable as it may seem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 769990.0,
      "end_time": 775081.0,
      "text": "we have no genetic toolkit  to ask the question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 775081.0,
      "end_time": 779744.0,
      "text": "Why are men, as a group,  at a higher or lower risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 779744.0,
      "end_time": 783794.0,
      "text": "of [suffering from] a particular disease, than women, as a group?"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 783794.0,
      "end_time": 786717.0,
      "text": "This is a big, big question"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 786717.0,
      "end_time": 791552.0,
      "text": "and to this point,  we have had no answers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 791552.0,
      "end_time": 795702.0,
      "text": "no systematic way of proceeding."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 795702.0,
      "end_time": 798916.0,
      "text": "But perhaps, just perhaps --"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 798916.0,
      "end_time": 802993.0,
      "text": "the answer has been staring at us  in the face all along."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 802993.0,
      "end_time": 808782.0,
      "text": "Because, of course, the individuals  who are prone to Autism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 808782.0,
      "end_time": 812519.0,
      "text": "and who tend to suffer more severely at an early age"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 812519.0,
      "end_time": 814409.0,
      "text": "from Dilated Cardiomyopathy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 814409.0,
      "end_time": 818656.0,
      "text": "those individuals are men and they are XY."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 818656.0,
      "end_time": 821522.0,
      "text": "And those individuals who disproportionately"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 821522.0,
      "end_time": 825159.0,
      "text": "suffer from Lups and Rheumatoid Arthritis, and a host of other diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 825159.0,
      "end_time": 826969.0,
      "text": "are women and they are XX."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 826969.0,
      "end_time": 832264.0,
      "text": "Of course, being XY versus XX is the most fundamental difference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 832264.0,
      "end_time": 834602.0,
      "text": "between males and females."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 834602.0,
      "end_time": 838407.0,
      "text": "But, the whole biomedical research enterprise"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 838407.0,
      "end_time": 842971.0,
      "text": "has been operating for decades  under the assumption"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 842971.0,
      "end_time": 847286.0,
      "text": "that the Y chromosome is operating"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 847286.0,
      "end_time": 850952.0,
      "text": "only within the cells of the reproductive tract"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 850952.0,
      "end_time": 854030.0,
      "text": "or, to frame it another way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 854030.0,
      "end_time": 859564.0,
      "text": "that the Y chromosome matters only in our nether parts."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 859564.0,
      "end_time": 862313.0,
      "text": "And, as an extension,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 862313.0,
      "end_time": 864693.0,
      "text": "the notion has been held firm"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 864693.0,
      "end_time": 868307.0,
      "text": "throughout the biomedical research enterprise  for decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 868307.0,
      "end_time": 871051.0,
      "text": "that all the differences between the sexes"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 871051.0,
      "end_time": 873938.0,
      "text": "outside the reproductive tract,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 873938.0,
      "end_time": 877350.0,
      "text": "including differences in disease susceptibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 877350.0,
      "end_time": 879624.0,
      "text": "outside the reproductive tract,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 879624.0,
      "end_time": 882682.0,
      "text": "the notion has been that all such differences"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 882682.0,
      "end_time": 886218.0,
      "text": "must stem from sex hormones"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 886218.0,
      "end_time": 891073.0,
      "text": "that are produced by the reproductive organs."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 891073.0,
      "end_time": 893991.0,
      "text": "But it turns out that in recent years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 893991.0,
      "end_time": 897946.0,
      "text": "my laboratory at the Whitehead Institute has discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 897946.0,
      "end_time": 900446.0,
      "text": "that the Y chromosome is functioning"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 900446.0,
      "end_time": 903306.0,
      "text": "not just in the reproductive organs"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 903306.0,
      "end_time": 906907.0,
      "text": "but actually, throughout the body."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 906907.0,
      "end_time": 910064.0,
      "text": "So that all the cells of your body --"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 910064.0,
      "end_time": 913505.0,
      "text": "the skin cells, the cells of your liver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 913505.0,
      "end_time": 916645.0,
      "text": "and of your heart, and even of your ear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 916645.0,
      "end_time": 921322.0,
      "text": "those cells know,  at a fundamental molecular level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 921322.0,
      "end_time": 926522.0,
      "text": "whether they are XX or XY."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 926522.0,
      "end_time": 930365.0,
      "text": "And the question that  I want to put before you is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 930365.0,
      "end_time": 932806.0,
      "text": "\"Does this matter?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 932806.0,
      "end_time": 937153.0,
      "text": "Does it matter outside the reproductive tract?"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 937153.0,
      "end_time": 940736.0,
      "text": "And I would like to suggest that it does matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 940736.0,
      "end_time": 946080.0,
      "text": "and it suggests a path forward towards a better health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 946080.0,
      "end_time": 950370.0,
      "text": "But how serious is the problem? Am I making this up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 950370.0,
      "end_time": 957983.0,
      "text": "Is the research enterprise really unaware of this reality?"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 957983.0,
      "end_time": 962929.0,
      "text": "Well, if I go to visit my research colleagues  around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 962929.0,
      "end_time": 968888.0,
      "text": "working in universities, in medical centers, in pharmaceutical companies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 968888.0,
      "end_time": 971447.0,
      "text": "If I got to ask colleagues around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 971447.0,
      "end_time": 976489.0,
      "text": "who are studying human cells, as shown here --"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 976489.0,
      "end_time": 981465.0,
      "text": "If I ask them, \"Are you studying XX cells or XY cells?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 981465.0,
      "end_time": 987417.0,
      "text": "The answer I get, almost always is -- \"I don't know.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 987417.0,
      "end_time": 992318.0,
      "text": "Well, if you don't know whether if you're studying XX or XY cells --"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 992318.0,
      "end_time": 997640.0,
      "text": "How could you possibly be taking account of this most fundamental difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 997640.0,
      "end_time": 1001951.0,
      "text": "between male and female cells,  tissues, organs and bodies?"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 1001950.0,
      "end_time": 1010413.0,
      "text": "And so -- it is the case that a great deal of the researchs being conducted today"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 1010410.0,
      "end_time": 1015214.0,
      "text": "with an eye towards  understanding the cause of disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 1015220.0,
      "end_time": 1019385.0,
      "text": "and identifying possible cures and treatments for disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 1019380.0,
      "end_time": 1024020.0,
      "text": "is failing to account for this most fundamental difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 1024020.0,
      "end_time": 1027321.0,
      "text": "between men and women."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 1027319.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1032863.9999999999,
      "text": "And it is for this reason that I said, somewhat provocatively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 1032869.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1037101.9999999999,
      "text": "at the beginning of this talk with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 1037099.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1041185.9999999999,
      "text": "that the study of disease is flawed."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 1041190.0,
      "end_time": 1046009.0,
      "text": "Well -- what to do? What can be done?"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 1046010.0,
      "end_time": 1049165.0,
      "text": "How can we think about this differently?"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 1049160.0,
      "end_time": 1054605.0,
      "text": "How can we think about  reconnecting and reconsidering"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 1054600.0,
      "end_time": 1057144.0,
      "text": "the link between sex and disease?"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 1057150.0,
      "end_time": 1061208.0,
      "text": "Well, here is what I think --"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 1061210.0,
      "end_time": 1067173.0,
      "text": "First of all, XX and XY cells do their business differently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 1067170.0,
      "end_time": 1073601.0,
      "text": "at the level of cells and all the higher levels of organization that follow."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 1073600.0,
      "end_time": 1076315.0,
      "text": "So, we need to take account,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 1076320.0,
      "end_time": 1079512.0,
      "text": "as researchers across the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 1079510.0,
      "end_time": 1082742.0,
      "text": "that there are, in fact,  fundamental differences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 1082740.0,
      "end_time": 1084421.0,
      "text": "not just in the reproductive tract,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 1084420.0,
      "end_time": 1086369.0,
      "text": "but throughout the body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 1086370.0,
      "end_time": 1090298.0,
      "text": "between XX and XY cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 1090300.0,
      "end_time": 1094515.0,
      "text": "We need to discover what those differences are."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 1094510.0,
      "end_time": 1097759.0,
      "text": "Already, in my laboratory at Whitehead Institute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 1097760.0,
      "end_time": 1100462.0,
      "text": "we are pursuing this question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 1100460.0,
      "end_time": 1102491.0,
      "text": "and already, we've discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 1102490.0,
      "end_time": 1107167.0,
      "text": "that XX and XY cells go about the business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 1107170.0,
      "end_time": 1113742.0,
      "text": "for example, of making proteins, in slightly different ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 1113740.0,
      "end_time": 1118312.0,
      "text": "Second, we need to build a better toolkit"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 1118320.0,
      "end_time": 1120717.0,
      "text": "for the scientists and the clinicians"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 1120710.0,
      "end_time": 1125611.0,
      "text": "who are pursuing cures and treatments for disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 1125610.0,
      "end_time": 1131021.0,
      "text": "We need to build a toolkit that is XX and XY informed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 1131030.0,
      "end_time": 1134705.0,
      "text": "rather than the present unisex toolkit."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 1134700.0,
      "end_time": 1138436.0,
      "text": "We need a toolkit that takes full recognition"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 1138440.0,
      "end_time": 1139731.0,
      "text": "of the fundamental differences"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 1139730.0,
      "end_time": 1145121.0,
      "text": "between XX and XY cells,  tissues, organs and bodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 1145120.0,
      "end_time": 1148929.0,
      "text": "And I believe that if we do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1148930.0,
      "end_time": 1151583.0,
      "text": "and I believe that we can,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1151580.0,
      "end_time": 1156517.0,
      "text": "that we will arrive at  a fundamentally new paradigm"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1156520.0,
      "end_time": 1160610.0,
      "text": "for understanding and  treating human disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1160610.0,
      "end_time": 1164760.0,
      "text": "so that, in the future, if you go to seek"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1164760.0,
      "end_time": 1168411.0,
      "text": "the help of a health care professional,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1168410.0,
      "end_time": 1170499.0,
      "text": "that it will in fact matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1170500.0,
      "end_time": 1173499.0,
      "text": "if you're a male or a female --"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1173500.0,
      "end_time": 1175773.0,
      "text": "the treatment that you receive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1175770.0,
      "end_time": 1178862.0,
      "text": "and not just, if you're going to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1178860.0,
      "end_time": 1183843.0,
      "text": "your gynecologist or your urologist."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1183840.0,
      "end_time": 1190752.0,
      "text": "So, in the future, this will transform"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1190760.0,
      "end_time": 1194074.0,
      "text": "the way we encounter the health care system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1194070.0,
      "end_time": 1197493.0,
      "text": "and I think that it will -- for you, and for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1197490.0,
      "end_time": 1201192.0,
      "text": "and for our children, and our grandchildren,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1201190.0,
      "end_time": 1204601.0,
      "text": "transform the experience of healthcare."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1204610.0,
      "end_time": 1214610.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}